# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
 
The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).
 
## [0.0.0] - 2025-01-31
 
### Added
- [TFM17-DEV-ENVIRONMENT-V1]() 
  MAJOR Created the base for the development environment.
 
### Changed
 
### Fixed

## [0.0.1] - 2025-02-06

### Added 
- [TFM17-DEV-ENVIRONMENT-V1]()
  MAJOR Completed and tested the base for development on Windows 11 using WSL 2.

### Changed

### Fixed

## [0.0.2] - 2025-02-15

### Added 
- [TFM17-DEV-ENVIRONMENT-V1]()
  MINOR Introduced utility scripts to ease working with Docker (using Portainer) in an Ubuntu 24.04 host.

### Changed

### Fixed
- [TFM17-DEV-ENVIRONMENT-V1]()
  MAJOR Completed and tested the base for development on Ubuntu 24.04 with X11 graphics passthrough.

## [0.0.3] - 2025-02-18

### Added
- [TFM17-DEV-ENVIRONMENT-V1](./_artifacts/)
  MAJOR Wrote documentation for scripts to create and save octomaps in `.bt` files using the standard ROS 2 OctoMap library installation. 
- [TFM17-DEV-ENVIRONMENT-V1](./_docs/) 
  MINOR Documented general observations about the environment.

### Changed
- [TFM17-DEV-ENVIRONMENT-V1](./_docs/Installing%20the%20OctoMap%20Library%20(Standalone).md)
  MAJOR Performed a standalone installation of the `devel` branch of the [OctoMap library](https://github.com/OctoMap/octomap).

### Fixed 

## [0.1.0] - 2025-02-19

### Added
- [CUSTOM-ROS2-PKGS]()
  MAJOR Implemented a custom node to save RGB color data associated to each node (voxel) in an octomap.
- [TFM17-UTILS]() 
  MAJOR Implemented scripts to automate octomap file format conversion.

### Changed
- [TFM17-DEV-ENVIRONMENT-V1]()
  MAJOR The execution of the environments's operations now depend on custom packages and utilities.

### Fixed 
- [TFM17-DEV-ENVIRONMENT-V1]()
  MINOR Fixed colored octomap visualization by switching the file format conversion from `.txt` > `.bt` to `.txt` > `.ot`, which can display color data.
